  {
    "hotel_id": "461846",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/mandarin-oriental-jakarta/hotel/jakarta-id.html",
    "name": "Mandarin Oriental, Jakarta",
    "detail": "I went on a business trip last week and was looking for a nice hotel around the Thamrin area. Mandarin came up first on TripAdvisor ranking for hotels in Jakarta, so I trust right away it could not be so bad. I was worried that it would be an old, boring hotel but I ended up being blown away by the classy design and comfort that the room offers. For superior type, the room is very (I mean very) spacey. It felt like a deluxe type or even more. The room is very much designed for business travellers, with work area and couches. The bathroom is nothing to be complained about either -and oh, there is a jacuzzi-like bath tub separated from the room with a glass window which makes the room feels even more spacious (you can close iy of course). My room was on a high floor and oversaw the HI roundabout, such a nice way to watch the city traffic in the comfort of luxury-class hotel. ",
